name: Design 2 - Wedding Monogram Personalized Stickers
description:
Monogram labels add elegance & style to your wedding events. Simply Embellish offers colorful personalized labels in a variety of sizes, designs & color that will add a personalized memorable touch to your wedding favors, gifts or invitations. These stickers are easy to use, just peel n’ stick! The labels are flat printed on a 8.5×11 sheet and packaged in a plastic sleeve This listing is for one sheet of personalized address labels, which will be laser printed on a high-quality matte label stock.
PLEASE CHOOSE ONE OF THE FOLLOWING ::SMALL:: - 24 Stickers - 1.67" round sticker ---------OR---------- ::MEDIUM:: - 12 Stickers - 2.5" round sticker ---------OR---------- ::LARGE:: - 6 Stickers - 3.33" round sticker

name: Retro Pink Gift Tag Essentials Set
description:
A box full of lots of little lovelies to add cheer to all of you holiday gift wrapping - whether it is homemade candy, a large box or a gift card.

Simplify your gift wrapping by using plain colored wrap and add these tags, stickers and little cards.


Included in this set: 

- 10 2x2" square tags
- 12 2x3.5" gift tags
- 12 1.67" round envelope seals
- 12 3x3.5" mailing labels
- 10 3.33" round gift tag labels
- 6 2" round scallop gift tags
